    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ようこそ、いらっしゃいました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You are most welcome in my domain.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今度こそ、本物……だよな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're the real one....right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ええ。
先ほどはアルテミスが
失礼をいたしました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Correct. I must apologize for
Artemis's attitude earlier.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ。それで……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's okay. In any case...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>用件はわかっています。
魔界の扉のことですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I understand what should be done.
We must prevent the Otherworldly
Gate from opening, correct?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あれはラグナロクの後、
魔界の王と精霊王の盟約により、
我が光の力で封じたものです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Back in the era of Ragnarok, the King of Daemonium
and the Lord of Summon Spirits convened that should
the time arise, my power of light would work as a seal.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ラグナロクって……
すげー気が遠く
なるような昔の話……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Era of Ragnarok, eh? I love
older stories like this!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298432</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その通りです。それだけに、
本来、人間が触れるべき
ではないもの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It is quite an interesting story. Perhaps
a little too much. In fact, humans are
forbidden from knowing such tales.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなたの力、
貸していただけるでしょうか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is it possible for you to lend
us your powers, then?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>受け取りなさい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Accept my power.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これを扉の前に掲げなさい。
我が光の力で扉は封印されます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hoist this once you face the door.
The might of my light should
suffice to seal it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それから
あなたたちが失った
精霊晶核ですが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As for you children, the
Atomism Cores you lost...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298944</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どこにあるか、
わかんのか！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You know where they are!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299096</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>マクスウェルの下へ
行きなさい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You must return to Maxwell.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299096</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>行き場をなくした精霊晶核は、
統括精霊の下へ集うのです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Should the Atomism Cores roam
freely they'll eventually return to
the Lord of the Four Elements.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299180</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うげ……
またマクスウェルか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Blech, not the old fart again...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299304</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>アルテミスの不手際で、
色々と面倒をかけましたね。
申し訳ありませんでした</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Artemis's pranks have caused
much trouble. I sincerely
apologize for his actions.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>い、いえ……
そんな……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>N-No, that's all right!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あのっ！　それかラっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>E-Excuse me! There's something
I must ask you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あなたが何者なのか、
ですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You want to know what manner
of being you are...don't you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい。ぼく……
ずっと自分のことを
妖精だと思ってて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes... All this time I thought I was a fairy...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうですね……
でも、あなたは
妖精ではありません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see... However, I am afraid it is 
not possible for you to be a fairy.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>では、何なのか……
そう問われても、
私にもわかりません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then what are you...? That's a question
I don't possess the answer to.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな……精霊でも
わからないなんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No... Not even a Summon Spirit knows...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299992</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お役に立てなくて、
すみません</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I apologize for not being of much help.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……
そうですか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, please...It's okay...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト、元気出して……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto, hang in there...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300272</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大丈夫だよ……うん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm fine...Yeah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300272</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_150_030_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん、
気にしない気にしない。
さ、行こうよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Okay, no more moping
around! Let's get moving!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
